        <detaileddescription>
<para>Controls a chained demuxer.</para>
<para>This performs a <bold>demux</bold> (i.e. DEMUX_...) control request on a chained demux.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>In most cases, vlc_demux_chained_Control() should be used instead. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="warning"><para>As per <ref refid="group__chained__demux_1ga2d69b8d5f935ebdd3dd1153f112959a0" kindref="member">vlc_demux_chained_New()</ref>, most demux controls are not, and cannot be, supported; VLC_EGENERIC is returned.</para>
</simplesect>
